Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要聽學姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我對於自己的逃跑本領還是挺有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}初次遇到的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}若妄想阻礙那孩子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後果 很嚴重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯

