Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑不動…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真奈美姐？為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那啥 我老公突然就叫我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請快開車 我被跟蹤狂纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跟蹤狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種傢伙我三拳兩腳就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀~~~~！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這跟蹤狂塊頭太大了~！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}追兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跟在後面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說什麼呢 搞不好都要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}越過這座山之後 馬上就到車站了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到那裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…還有？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}靈奈？！不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為有反連環力場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(664,662)}anti-field
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以只能幫到這點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快去吧 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少 不要留下悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那傢伙…還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們走吧 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣就能到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是因為…我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學 北原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家都想實現學姐的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算是為了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也要到達那個地方 找到外星人留有的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話 學姐就能不用回宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家就能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒問題 一定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果 一切都順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終有一天 我們也能去學姐的星球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那當然有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐是在什麼樣的地方生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家裡都有什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想知道 也想見一見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也想介紹給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你會怎麼介紹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也想把學姐介紹給我父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 我父母的事已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我還有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有時會想要是能再多創造些回憶就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 所以我才會用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}記錄下許多的…各種各樣的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即便是些瑣事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但為了之後不留下遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡面包含著海人的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 穀川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原 檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家都在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可是女主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得我來到這個星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}與大家相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起玩耍 一起拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這些都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}若是能一直這樣…讓這個夏天永不結束那該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著…這麼些事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知不覺間 海人就成了我的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐也在我的正中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不光只有開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也有過讓人難受的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又是生氣 又是哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從今往後也會有各種各樣的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說不定還會吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到時你會怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對會和好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要懷著「喜歡」的這份心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼困難都能夠克服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你會一直…喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也愛上了海人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會一直喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才說的那個 請再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會一直喜歡海人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也要一直…喜歡我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過啊 我還不能放棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲…哲朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉了 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒油了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那聲音 難道是聰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聰叔是指…真奈美姐的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快來救我啊 聰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要被侵犯了啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然不太清楚 但就這麼一直衝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留在我印象中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終於抵達了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終於找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們去找遺留下的痕跡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就是外星人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這反應果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你能看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可…這是我印象中的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是在治療的時候使用了我的細胞的緣故嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留下的痕跡難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好不容易才…好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是一夏他們所去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}空間的遮罩被打破了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不妙啊一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要傷害他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不會再逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓海人 讓大家深陷險境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是因為我太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這樣的 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家 至少我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從沒有那麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不如說這是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不想讓你走 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我曾經…後悔過我來到這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由於我的一廂情願將大家捲了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結果卻一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們 因為都想要開始一段什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而找到了對方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順利的找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}孕育我心中的 這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會一直持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能夠相信…它絕不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都…一直
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會去接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定會去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:26.85,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}這個謎の聲的聲優是井上喜久子 拜託了老師中女主角風間瑞穗的聲優
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}有多少時光流淌而去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}謝謝你能找到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…能夠直接從因克拉布聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}繼承下來的祖先的資料 被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}我從宇宙而來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}在這個星球迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}得到了這個星球的居民的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}不知不覺 那個人成為了我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}但這裡是不允許與原住民接觸的邊境行星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}不久就會有人來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}為了保持秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}在這星球的記憶也會被封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}都想將和那個人一起的記憶留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}即便我失去了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}再也無法想起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}都想要將它留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}謝謝你 找到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}我的記憶至少能成為你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}拜託你 不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼可能會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會一直…等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那僅僅是在幾個月之間所發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個夏天的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的我們 還什麼都沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是想要做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那時 一夏學姐出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}將我們的夏天…變得如此特別
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜悅與哀痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}概其總總
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(300,300)}不會忘懷 那難忘的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隔壁班的女生拜託我給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要收下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒辦法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要好好回覆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 你也差不多去給我交個女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻就不錯了啊 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隨時歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…那個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別笑啊 海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？我忘了上鎖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玻利維亞怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給 土特產
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這品位沒問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 這能實現願望的人偶在那邊挺有名的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 這是一夏醬的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說一夏醬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐她…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留學結束了 回故鄉去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那寄過去給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}地址知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}願望嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}轉校嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 因為家庭原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣…要是連檸檬學姐都不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那什麼時候轉學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然算不上餞別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個送給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}膠捲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是個美妙的夏天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影還沒有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要為最終幕畫下句點的 是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然就跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 今天姐姐會晚點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 真是久違了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家聚在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那關燈咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開始放了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}據說人死後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就能登入極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我卻不這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}逝者的生命一定在生者的心間旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}化為回憶…流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這些也終將消卻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以人們才會想留下些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了不被忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了不忘記它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直都轉動著攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}烙印在膠捲裡的那個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}它的續篇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今年也有放啊 這個電影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是畢業生留下的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去年看了 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:22:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}宇宙船呀 機械什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特效可真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有女主角是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結果你在意的是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有住的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要來我家住嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一個人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家裡有很多空房
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 宇宙船怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈 壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝大家為我們加油打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝！
Comment: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:49.67,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(876,692)}白月和DHR期待與你再次相遇

Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:04.69,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,越過鏡片所窺視的世界{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:12.89,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,像是事不關己那般映照而出{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:19.05,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,當我知曉那失卻的感情時{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:27.54,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的時間 開始運轉{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:35.08,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,用天平所衡量的戀愛的品質{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:41.26,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都配不平呢{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:45.44,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,天空的形體 烙印而上{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.95,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,直通到銀河的彼岸{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:56.25,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,那斑駁的日光 那份溫度 我想擁有它們的全部{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.85,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,卻曾有過的 那個夏天{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.42,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,將稚嫩的回憶{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:12.71,--ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,塵封於此 像是向著遠方 向著大海而去{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:47.33,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}我曾一直追尋 喜歡上你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:55.52,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}若要為它飾上最合適的言語 那大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:20:02.21,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}當我悄然發覺時 心緒早已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:10.71,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}緊繫於你 愈纏愈緊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:18.23,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HCD6A1D&\t(2864,3156,\3c&H0090FF)}若我不曾躊躇 對你說出那句話來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:24.36,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HDB6CEB&\t(2551,3000,\3c&H77BD3E)}你已經不哭了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:28.35,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}越過流雲的浮影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.00,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}繪出想你的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:39.28,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}在彌漫著盛夏的芳香之中 無數次浮現出你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:42.97,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}是誰曾觸及那輪軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:47.73,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}像夏日午後滴咚下落的雷陣雨那般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:55.66,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}點上一抹新色
